title: Shang Pin Zhai
description: Noodle shop serving vegetables, miso, and rice that are organic. Options include hand-pulled noodle, rice vermicelli, or yang chun (Canton) noodle; noodle in soup, "dry" noodle, or pan-fried noodle; with or without dumplings (wonton); in base of miso, herbs, or Sichuan vegetable. Has an English menu but no English on signage - look for sign with 上品齋 and the English phrase "organic vegetables and rice". NOTE: On Google Maps the street is spelled "QingNian", but the actual street sign uses "CingNian."
